{"name": "protobase-client", "metadata": {"name": "protobase-client", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/AkiTheMemeGod/ProtoBase", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests"], "summary": "A Python client for the ProtoBase authentication API", "upload_time": 1735457296}, "documentation": ["# ProtoBase Client\r\n\r\nA Python client for the ProtoBase authentication API that supports email and username sign-up/sign-in.\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npip install protobase-client\r\n```\r\n## Usage\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom protobase_client import ProtoBaseClient\r\n\r\nclient = ProtoBaseClient()\r\n\r\n# Sign up with email\r\nsignup_response = client.signup_email(\"username\", \"password\", \"email@example.com\")\r\nprint(signup_response)\r\n\r\n# Sign in with email\r\nsignin_response = client.signin_email(\"username\", \"password\", \"email@example.com\")\r\nprint(signin_response)\r\n\r\n# Sign up with username\r\nsignup_response = client.signup_username(\"username\", \"password\")\r\nprint(signup_response)\r\n\r\n# Sign in with username\r\nsignin_response = client.signin_username(\"username\", \"password\")\r\nprint(signin_response)\r\n\r\n```\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "protobase_client", "documentation": ["protobase_client/__init__.py"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "protobase_client.ProtoBaseClient", "xref": {"fqname": "protobase_client.auth.ProtoBaseClient", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "protobase_client.auth", "documentation": ["protobase_client/auth.py"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "protobase_client.auth.BASE_URL", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "protobase_client.auth.ProtoBaseClient", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "protobase_client.auth.ProtoBaseClient.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "p